717
00:46:07,931 --> 00:46:08,974
Something like that.

718
00:46:10,267 --> 00:46:12,811
He's a far greater artist than I thought.

719
00:46:19,067 --> 00:46:21,695
Make sure everything is set up.

720
00:46:21,778 --> 00:46:25,199
Make sure to check everything
thoroughly at the scene.

721
00:46:25,282 --> 00:46:27,117
And as for Myeong-ho, I want you to…

