00:51:29,795 --> 00:51:31,254
Hi, Ye-in.

753
00:51:31,338 --> 00:51:33,673
You should go home.
You have a big day tomorrow.

754
00:51:33,757 --> 00:51:36,676
You should go get some rest too.
Good work today.

755
00:51:38,678 --> 00:51:42,766
How much do you think Go-oh did so far?

756
00:51:43,642 --> 00:51:44,851
Do you think he succeeded?

757
00:51:46,228 --> 00:51:49,064
I'm sure he did.

758
00:51:50,232 --> 00:51:53,401
I bet he didn't even have time
to sleep or eat.

759
00:51:54,736 --> 00:51:56,363
Being an artist must be difficult.

760
00:51:57,030 --> 00:51:58,907
I'll get going then.

